Theme Description:

New Windows 7 Theme specially for you! I know that a big number of us watch House MD Series and love it so i created this special House M.D Windows 7 Theme to all those who adore it and this House M.D Windows 7 Theme includes:
- 20 House M.D beautiful wallpaper collected by me.
- Medical Icons as appeared in the preview above.
- Ubuntu cool Cursors.
- House M.D sounds consist of: heart beat, i am Dr House, House Series Theme, House M.D exit and vocal every bodies lies.
- to install all of this just click on the thempack
